{"comments":"Canvas Render Objects — Object rendering functions.\n\n## Purpose\n\nRenders individual canvas objects with proper compositing:\n- Basic object rendering\n- Full compositing (blend mode, opacity, visibility)\n\n## Compositing Order\n\nObjects are rendered with:\n1. Position and bounds\n2. Blend mode (CSS mix-blend-mode)\n3. Opacity\n4. Visibility\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Canvas.Types (CanvasObject)\n- Render.Types (RenderConfig, CanvasMsg)\n- Render.Helpers (blendModeToCSS, showObjectId)\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Render a single object.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Canvas","Types","Object"],"CanvasObject"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Element","Types"],"Element"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Canvas","Render","Types"],"CanvasMsg"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[55,58],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Canvas/Render/Objects.purs","start":[55,1]},"title":"renderObject"},{"children":[],"comments":"Render object with full compositing.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Canvas","Render","Types"],"RenderConfig"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","Canvas","Types","Object"],"CanvasObject"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"t